                "text": "As a full action, a xararian mystic who has at least one free hand can replace any one of their spells known with a new spell of the same level contained within their spell tome. A typical xararian thaumaturge\u2019s spell tome contains the following additional spells at the associated levels\u2014<i>animate dead</i> (4th), <i>enervation</i> (4th), <i>feeblemind</i> (5th), <i>mystic cure</i> (4th through 6th), <i>raise dead</i> (5th), and <i>waves of fatigue</i> (5th).",
